[p]Ahoy Victorians, a small hotfix today fixing the issue where aristocrats were very very poor and a bug with on_election_campaign_end not being called.
[/p][p]Check out the full patchnotes below. Checksum is `6093`.
[/p][p]As always please report any bugs on [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/forums/victoria-3-bug-reports.1114/"]our bug reporting forums[/url][/u]! We have also updated the [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/known-issues-update-1-10.1859597/"]Known Issues post for 1.10[/url][/u] with any fixed issues!
[/p][p]The following changes have been made to the game compared to 1.10.3:[/p][h2]Bugfixes[/h2][list][*][p]Fixed a bug that applies subsistence farm penalty multiplier when calculating starting wage so the poor hardworking aristocrats don't starve[/p][/*][*][p]Fixed a bug with on_election_campaign_end not being called[/p][p][/p][/*][/list][p][b]Previous Patchnotes[/b][/p][p][u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/developer-diary/victoria-3-dev-diary-160-national-awakening-update-1-10-now-live.1859612/"]1.10.0[/url][/u] | [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-10-1-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1860263/"]1.10.1[/url][/u] | [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-10-2-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1860447/"]1.10.2[/url][/u] | [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-10-3-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1861262/"]1.10.3[/url][/u][/p]